::Killfest::

Killfest opens his mouth to comment on the treaty, but then the 
Decepticon rushes Angel Prime. He smiles to himself and then turns 
around, his EMP gun aimed at Angel Prime's chest. Without commend, 
Killfest fires three blasts from it at Angel Prime.
